```{r setup, include = FALSE}
library(datos)
library(ggplot2)
library(dplyr)
knitr::opts_chunk$set(fig.width = 5, fig.asp = 1 / 3, echo = FALSE)
```

## Columna 1

### Quilate

```{r}
ggplot(diamantes, aes(quilate)) + geom_histogram(binwidth = 0.1)
```

### Corte

```{r}
ggplot(diamantes, aes(corte)) + geom_bar()
```

### Color

```{r}
ggplot(diamantes, aes(color)) + geom_bar()
```

## Columna 2

### Diamantes mÃ¡s grandes

```{r}
diamantes %>%
  arrange(desc(quilate)) %>%
  head(100) %>%
  select(quilate, corte, color, precio) %>%
  DT::datatable()
```